prompts.frontCover:
A vibrant and whimsical greeting card front cover, illustrated in a flat 2D dreamy fantasy art style. The scene is set in an enchanted, magical forest clearing under a twilight sky filled with pastel swirls of lavender, peach, and mint green. Glowing motes of light and tiny, twinkling stars float in the air.

At the center of the composition are cartoon-illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo.

Lao Lao, on the left, is illustrated with a mischievous, joyful grin. She is depicted floating slightly off the ground, gleefully holding a giant, comically oversized, sparkling birthday cake that is covered in glowing candles and whimsical, magical decorations. She wears her white dress from the photo.

Jordan, on the right, looks up at the floating cake with a humorous expression of surprised delight. He's also illustrated floating slightly, as if lifted by magical energy, and is wearing his graduation gown and colorful lei from the photo, but his graduation cap is floating just above his head at a jaunty angle.

The background features fantastical, oversized mushrooms with glowing spots, and trees with shimmering, iridescent leaves. The overall feeling is magical, ethereal, and playfully chaotic.

Centered on the card, in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Jordan!"
